metadata.name: The Korean War : Ghosts are crying
metadata.description:
We've lost a lot of things.
We've lost a lot of value.
Most of the families broke up and the children starved to death.
Fight for what?
People? or Ideology?
Will peace like a river come to us?

Please SAVE US FROM KOREAN WAR
